---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Supported Independent Living - Ossified Orbit">
	<div class="page-container">
		<h1>Supported Independent Living</h1>
		<div class="hero-section">
			<p>Empowering individuals to live independently while providing the support and resources needed to thrive in their own homes and communities.</p>
		</div>
		
		<div class="content-sections">
			<section class="service-section">
				<h2>Independence with Support</h2>
				<p>Our Supported Independent Living program bridges the gap between residential care and complete independence. We provide flexible, individualized support that allows people to live in their own homes while accessing the services they need to maintain stability and achieve their personal goals.</p>
			</section>
			
			<section class="service-section">
				<h2>Core Services</h2>
				<div class="services-grid">
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Daily Living Skills</h3>
						<p>Training and support in essential life skills including cooking, cleaning, budgeting, and personal care management.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Community Integration</h3>
						<p>Assistance connecting with community resources, social activities, and building meaningful relationships.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Employment Support</h3>
						<p>Job search assistance, interview preparation, workplace skills training, and ongoing employment support.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Healthcare Coordination</h3>
						<p>Help navigating healthcare systems, managing appointments, and ensuring continuity of medical and mental health care.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Crisis Planning</h3>
						<p>Development of personalized crisis intervention plans and 24/7 access to emergency support when needed.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="service-card">
						<h3>Life Coaching</h3>
						<p>Goal setting, motivation, and ongoing coaching to help individuals achieve their personal and professional aspirations.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			
			<section class="service-section">
				<h2>Program Features</h2>
				<div class="features-container">
					<div class="feature-column">
						<h3>Flexible Support Levels</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Daily check-ins and visits</li>
							<li>Weekly support meetings</li>
							<li>Monthly progress reviews</li>
							<li>As-needed crisis support</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-column">
						<h3>Individualized Plans</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Personal goal development</li>
							<li>Customized service delivery</li>
							<li>Progress tracking and adjustments</li>
							<li>Regular plan reviews</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="feature-column">
						<h3>Community Focus</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>Local resource connections</li>
							<li>Social skill development</li>
							<li>Volunteer opportunities</li>
							<li>Peer support networks</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
			
			<section class="service-section">
				<h2>Who Benefits</h2>
				<p>Our Supported Independent Living program serves adults who have the desire and potential to live independently but need ongoing support to maintain housing, employment, and community connections. This includes individuals transitioning from residential care, those with mental health conditions, developmental disabilities, or anyone seeking to build greater independence while maintaining necessary supports.</p>
			</section>
			
			<section class="service-section cta">
				<h2>Take the Next Step</h2>
				<p>Ready to explore greater independence with the right support? Learn more about our Supported Independent Living program and how we can help you achieve your goals.</p>
				<a href="/contact" class="cta-button">Learn More</a>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-container {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1rem;
		width: 1000px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2rem);
		color: #000000;
		font-size: 20px;
		line-height: 1.6;
	}
	
	h1 {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	
	.hero-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		padding: 2rem;
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
	}
	
	.hero-section p {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		margin: 0;
		color: #f39c12;
	}
	
	.content-sections {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}
	
	.service-section h2 {
		color: #f39c12;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-size: 2rem;
	}
	
	.service-section p {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}
	
	.services-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}
	
	.service-card {
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
		transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
	}
	
	.service-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.2);
	}
	
	.service-card h3 {
		color: #e67e22;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
	}
	
	.service-card p {
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.5;
		margin: 0;
	}
	
	.features-container {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 2rem;
	}
	
	.feature-column {
		background: rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.05);
		padding: 2rem;
		border-radius: 8px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.2);
	}
	
	.feature-column h3 {
		color: #f39c12;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
	}
	
	.feature-column ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}
	
	.feature-column li {
		padding: 0.5rem 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
		font-size: 1rem;
	}
	
	.feature-column li:last-child {
		border-bottom: none;
	}
	
	.feature-column li::before {
		content: "âœ“";
		color: #f39c12;
		font-weight: bold;
		margin-right: 0.5rem;
	}
	
	.cta {
		text-align: center;
		background: rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.1);
		padding: 3rem;
		border-radius: 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.3);
	}
	
	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		background: #f39c12;
		color: #000000;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
		border-radius: 6px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-weight: bold;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
		transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
	}
	
	.cta-button:hover {
		background: #e67e22;
		transform: translateY(-2px);
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		h1 {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}
		
		.hero-section p {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}
		
		.services-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
		
		.features-container {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>